{
  "texts": [
    "Next, we will cover popular deep learning methods in AES and discuss their fundamental architecture.",
    "Then, we will provide a thorough discussion on AES tasks, specifically exploring recent research categorized as holistic scoring and trait-specific scoring for prompt-specific and cross-domain prompts, as well as automated feedback generation.",
    "This work also includes widely used datasets and performance measurement metrics in AES studies.",
    "Finally, we will present the challenges and research directions in AES tasks.",
    "AES task can be broadly divided into two phases: essay representation and essay scoring."
  ]
}